sequenceDiagram
    participant Coordinator as MAP Coordinator
    participant Broadcaster as Agent (Broadcaster)
    participant A1 as Agent A1
    participant A2 as Agent A2
    participant A3 as Agent A3

    Note over Coordinator: MAPSessionStarted
    Coordinator->>Broadcaster: Assign broadcast role
    Coordinator->>A1: Assign responder role
    Coordinator->>A2: Assign responder role
    Coordinator->>A3: Assign responder role
    Note over Coordinator: MAPRolesAssigned

    Broadcaster->>Coordinator: Broadcast message/task
    Note over Coordinator: MAPBroadcastSent

    par Parallel Response Collection
        A1->>Coordinator: Response 1
        Note over Coordinator: MAPBroadcastReceived (A1)
    and
        A2->>Coordinator: Response 2
        Note over Coordinator: MAPBroadcastReceived (A2)
    and
        A3->>Coordinator: Response 3
        Note over Coordinator: MAPBroadcastReceived (A3)
    end

    Coordinator->>Broadcaster: Aggregated results
    Note over Coordinator: MAPSessionCompleted
